<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <title></title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Henny+Penny&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="meal.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.4.1/css/bootstrap.min.css" integrity="sha384-Vkoo8x4CGsO3+Hhxv8T/Q5PaXtkKtu6ug5TOeNV6gBiFeWPGFN9MuhOf23Q9Ifjh" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.4.1/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <script type="text/javascript" src="jquery-3.5.1.js"></script>
</head>

<body>
    <section>
        <div class="header">
            <h1 class="xyz">Eat or Get Eaten</h1>
        </div>

        <div class="row" style="padding:7%; background-color:#bbbfca"">
            <div class="col-lg-6">
                <h1>Grandma Witch</h1>
                <p>Grandma Witch loves to cook meals for the house vistors. She has an experience of more than 13 years in cooking at the Cannibal Hut. Make sure you taste all her Halloween Specials because Grandma don't want you to go outta here with an empty stomach. (P.S.-Do not believe the rumours. There's no such thing as a man-eating monster.)</p>
               
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-6">
                <script src="https://unpkg.com/@lottiefiles/lottie-player@latest/dist/lottie-player.js"></script>
                <lottie-player src="https://assets8.lottiefiles.com/packages/lf20_aG0HWp.json"  background="transparent"  speed="1"  style="width: 100%; height: 300px;"  loop  autoplay></lottie-player>
            </div>
        </div>
       

        <div class="row" style="padding:7%; background-color:#e8e8e8">
            <div class="col-lg-6">
                <script src="https://unpkg.com/@lottiefiles/lottie-player@latest/dist/lottie-player.js"></script>
                <lottie-player src="https://assets5.lottiefiles.com/packages/lf20_yiasudjv.json"  background="transparent"  speed="1"  style="width: 100%; height: 300px;"  loop  autoplay></lottie-player>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-6">
                <h1>Eyeball Soup</h1>
                <p>Start your meal with a big bowl of our Eyeball Soup. Hand-picked eyeballs of the darkest frogs and lizards, boiled in snake juice and garnished with cobwebs.</p>
                <audio id="audio1" src="slurp.wav" autoplay="false" ></audio>
                <center><button class="btn btn-light btn-lg" onclick="playSound1();">Taste!</button></center>
                <script>
                function playSound1() {
                    var sound1 = document.getElementById("audio1");
                    sound1.play();
                }
                </script>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row" style="padding:7%;background-color:#bbbfca">

            <div class="col-lg-6">
                <script src="https://unpkg.com/@lottiefiles/lottie-player@latest/dist/lottie-player.js"></script>
                <lottie-player src="https://assets2.lottiefiles.com/packages/lf20_uyk1c026.json"  background="transparent"  speed="1"  style="width: 100%; height: 300px;"  loop  autoplay></lottie-player>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-6">
                <h1>Slime Wine</h1>
                <p>Only the best slime collected from around the graveyard with fermented bat squeezings. Mix it with an equal amount of cockroach blood and consume.</p>
                <audio id="audio2" src="wine.mp3" autoplay="false" ></audio>
                <center><button class="btn btn-light btn-lg" onclick="playSound2();">Drink!</button></center>
                <script>
                function playSound2() {
                    var sound2 = document.getElementById("audio2");
                    sound2.play();
                }
                </script>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row" style="padding:7%; background-color:#e8e8e8">
            <div class="col-lg-6">
                <script src="https://unpkg.com/@lottiefiles/lottie-player@latest/dist/lottie-player.js"></script>
                <lottie-player src="https://assets3.lottiefiles.com/packages/lf20_oBHf8y.json"  background="transparent"  speed="1"  style="width: 100%; height: 300px;"  loop  autoplay></lottie-player>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-6">
                <h1>Bones Porridge</h1>
                <p>No one can make a porridge as delicious as Grandma's, out of crushed animal eggs and chopped shark meat, served hot with tangy bone crispies.</p>
                <audio id="audio3" src="chew.mp3" autoplay="false" ></audio>
                <center><button class="btn btn-light btn-lg" onclick="playSound3();">Eat!</button></center>
                <script>
                function playSound3() {
                    var sound3 = document.getElementById("audio3");
                    sound3.play();
                }
                </script>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div style="padding:10%; background-color:#bbbfca;">
            <h1>How was the meal?</h1>
                <audio id="audioMmm" src="yummy.mp3" autoplay="false" ></audio>
                <button style="display:inline-block; margin:4%" class="btn btn-light btn-lg" onclick="playSoundMmm()">Mmmm delicious!</button>
                <script>
                function playSoundMmm() {
                    var soundMmm = document.getElementById("audioMmm");
                    soundMmm.play();
                }
                </script>

                <audio id="audioUgh" src="monster-eat.wav" autoplay="false" ></audio>
                <button style="display:inline-block; margin:4%" class="btn btn-light btn-lg" onclick="playSoundUgh(); location.href='#monster';">Ugh disgusting!</button>
                <script>
                function playSoundUgh() {
                    var soundUgh = document.getElementById("audioUgh");
                    soundUgh.play();
                }
                </script>        
        </div>

        <div id="monster" style="background-color:#495464;  padding-bottom:5%; position: relative;">
            <script src="https://unpkg.com/@lottiefiles/lottie-player@latest/dist/lottie-player.js"></script>
            <lottie-player src="https://assets1.lottiefiles.com/packages/lf20_nBze2y.json"  background="transparent"  speed="1"  style="width: 100%; height: 300px;"  loop  autoplay></lottie-player>
            <h1>Uh Oh! Grandma fed you to the Slime monster!</h1>
        </div>
      

    </section>
    
</body>


